graph TB
    subgraph OGXOperator["OGX Kubernetes Operator"]
        Controller["OGXServer Reconciler<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        Webhook["Validating Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
        ManifestPipeline["Manifest Rendering Pipeline<br/>(kustomize + Go plugins)"]
        ConfigGen["Declarative Config Generator<br/>(base + merge)"]
        LegacyAdoption["Legacy Adoption Handler<br/>(LlamaStack → OGX)"]

        Controller -->|renders via| ManifestPipeline
        Controller -->|generates| ConfigGen
        Controller -->|delegates| LegacyAdoption
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    %% CRDs
    OGXServerCR["OGXServer CR<br/>(ogx.io/v1beta1)"]
    LegacyCR["LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>(llamastack.io/v1alpha1)<br/>(read-only)"]

    OGXServerCR -->|watched by| Controller
    LegacyCR -.->|adopted by| LegacyAdoption

    %% Managed Resources
    subgraph ManagedResources["Managed Resources (per OGXServer)"]
        Deployment["Deployment"]
        Service["Service<br/>8321/TCP"]
        PVC["PersistentVolumeClaim"]
        NetworkPolicy["NetworkPolicy"]
        PDB["PodDisruptionBudget"]
        HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler"]
        Ingress["Ingress<br/>(optional)"]
        SA["ServiceAccount"]
        RB["RoleBinding<br/>(anyuid SCC)"]
        GenConfigMap["Generated ConfigMap<br/>(content-hashed)"]
    end

    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| Deployment
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| Service
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| PVC
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| NetworkPolicy
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| PDB
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| HPA
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| SA
    ManifestPipeline -->|creates/updates| RB
    Controller -->|creates/updates| Ingress
    ConfigGen -->|creates| GenConfigMap

    %% External Dependencies
    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"]
    OCIRegistry["OCI Container Registries<br/>(quay.io, docker.io)"]
    CertManager["cert-manager /<br/>service-serving-cert-signer"]

    Controller -->|REST API| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|OCI label fetch| OCIRegistry
    CertManager -->|provisions TLS| Webhook

    %% Platform Integration
    ODHTrustedCA["odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap"]
    OperatorConfig["ogx-operator-config<br/>ConfigMap"]
    Monitoring["monitoring.coreos.com<br/>ServiceMonitor / PrometheusRule"]

    Controller -->|auto-detects| ODHTrustedCA
    Controller -->|reads overrides| OperatorConfig
    Controller -->|conditionally creates| Monitoring

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ManifestPipeline fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ConfigGen fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LegacyAdoption fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OGXServerCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LegacyCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style OCIRegistry fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ODHTrustedCA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OperatorConfig fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
